{"about_the_game":"TrainFormation is a simple, fast-paced puzzle game created by one student as a university project. Place rails in front of an ever-accelerating train to cross procedurally generated levels, reach stations, collect power ups and make it as far as you can!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Build a path for the train</h2>Swap hexagonal tiles to create a path for the train. Make sure to find the matching rails and terrain, or the train will not make it through! <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u2800</ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077150/extras/Shop_GIF_1.gif?t=1660911218\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Reach stations and collect power ups</h2>Make it to a station and take a moment to breathe. Use specific rail tiles to collect power ups to help you in your toughest moments!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u2800</ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077150/extras/Shop_GIF_2.gif?t=1660911218\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Make it as far as you can</h2>Reach new levels and face the difficult terrain. Hold on tight as the train continues to accelerate!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">\u2800</ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2077150/extras/Shop_GIF_3.gif?t=1660911218\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"KABOOM!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2077150/18e71e24de35294b02552305ca18506ab333426a.jpg"},{"name":"Watch out for the cliffs!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2077150/7c69e7343b73496db241f5c1881044834e2637ba.jpg"},{"name":"Fishing not allowed","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2077150/a8d71ce01c99cbf302694aad03d12ef4715bcb3e.jpg"},{"name":"You know there are other power ups, right?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2077150/a7ee9